          </h4>

          <ul class="space-y-4 mt-4">
            <li>Led development for the lab's high-profile external <Link href="https://jhuapl.edu/2021-Annual-Report" target="_blank">Annual</Link> and <Link href="https://jhuapl.edu/Diversity-Inclusion-Annual-Report-2021" target="_blank">DE&I</Link> interactive reports</li>
